feedback.response: The app's interface is clean and intuitive. I love how easy it is to browse through different restaurants.
The reservation system is very reliable. I've never had any issues booking a table.
The app crashes frequently when trying to view restaurant photos. This needs to be fixed.
Menu prices are not always up to date. I've been surprised by different prices at the restaurant.
The search filters are excellent! I can easily find exactly what I'm looking for.
The app takes too long to load restaurant details. It's frustrating when I'm in a hurry.
I love the feature that shows nearby restaurants based on my location. Very convenient!
The reviews section is not moderated well. There are many fake reviews.
The offline mode works great! I can still access my saved restaurants without internet.
The app doesn't remember my dietary preferences between sessions. Annoying to set them up each time.
The dark mode feature is perfect for late-night browsing. Easy on the eyes!
The app's notification system is too aggressive. I get too many alerts.
The restaurant recommendations are spot-on! Always find great new places.
The app freezes when trying to upload photos of my dining experience.
The loyalty program integration is fantastic. Great rewards!
The app uses too much battery life. Needs optimization.

The app doesn't support split payments for group reservations.
